subSubSection.paragraph:
Tergites
: smooth, with scattered setae and punctuation. Tergite 1 with an anterior transverse suture (
Fig. 12
). Tergite 2 with intricate transverse suture (
Fig. 19
); TT3–5 and TT20–22 with incomplete paramedian sutures, TT6– 19 with complete paramedian sutures (
Figs 6
, 
14
); TT5–23 with complete margination. Posterior part of the tergite of ultimate leg-bearing segment with a low median longitudinal depression and posterior margin with trapezoid protrusion (
Figs 14, 15
).

