subSubSection.paragraph:
Sternites
: smooth, with a few minute setae and scattered punctuation, without suture (
Figs 7
, 
13
). Sternite of ultimate leg-bearing segment with sides converging posteriorly and longer than wide (length: 
2.15 mm
), basal part broad (width: 
1.80 mm
), distal part narrow (width: 
0.55 mm
), posterior margin slightly concave in the middle (
Fig. 17
).

